    public class NetworkImpl<TBus extends Bus,TBranch extends Branch>
extends NameTagImpl
implements Network<TBus,TBranch>
    An implementation of the model object 'work'.

    The following features are implemented:

    • Base Kva
    • Frequency
    • Bus Number Arranged
    • Data Checked
    • Bypass Data Check
    • Allow Ground Branch
    • Switch Break Model
    • Original Data Format
    • Ref Bus Type
    • Ref Bus Id
    • Branch List
    • Bus List
    • Zone List
    • Area List
    • Tie Line List
    • Owner List
    • Child Net List
